<h2><span><span style="color: blue">Note: If you're going to introduce yourself here, please scroll down and click &quot;New Post&quot; and NOT &quot;reply&quot;, otherwise your comment will nest incorrectly!</span></span></h2>
<p>Hello, new site members/artists/gamers/social media watchers/roleplayers/etc.!</p>
<h3><span>This month's random question is: would you keep a miniature version of your favorite SCP in your house? Why or why not?</span></h3>
<p>Here's some places to talk to get you all started off, now that you've arrived:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/c-1900210/games-and-hobbies">Games and Hobbies forum</a></strong>: Just started playing a new game or are wondering if any other SCP site members play your favorite game? Alternatively, wondering if anyone else paints minifigures or goes to conventions? Jump into the conversations here.</li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/c-1900211/media-discussion">Media Discussion forum</a></strong>: Have a cool video or news article that just <em>screams</em> of the paranormal? Talk about it and other such things here!</li>
<li><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/c-662937/fan-work">Fan Work forum</a></strong>: Have a cool drawing or want to see the work of some of the other artists here? Have an SCP-based mod or board game in the works? This is the place to discuss!</li>
</ul>
<p>If you're not sure what to talk about here, you can take a look at our <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-985304/how-to-write-an-intro-or-welcome">How to Write an Intro/Welcome</a> thread for ideas.</p>
<p>Have fun mingling with the other new arrivals and talking about your interests, hobbies, and plans for taking over the universe. You might also see some of our veteran users here from time to time, since you never know when someone might be looking for an artist or a voice actor or an idea-haver for the next big collaboration article or SCP project! Talk and be merry. :)</p>
<p>Welcome to the site!</p>

